name: MSRI-QUADRO-GIFYGBV-R-01
description: v4w.enko - "MSRI-QUADRO-GIFYGBV-R-01" is a gif animation of  3d Object, generated with custom definition. 4 lofts are animated in 4 layers for each color: Yellow, Green, Blue, Violet. The cells of the Red  "3d voronoi" cube are linked to the attractor`s points of the lofts. The parallel projections are showing the different viewpoints of the same form. Top, Bottom, Back, Right. Total 128 frames, 1024*1024px canvas.
